Vale SA (VALE3)  Chief Executive Officer
Murilo Ferreira said the Brazilian company will initiate its $6
billion potash project in Argentina. He spoke today from the
presidential palace in Buenos Aires.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Pablo Gonzalez in Buenos Aires at 
